description: This still will share facts about Georgia Tech traditions. Information included in this skill can be found at http://www.gatech.edu/about/history-and-traditions and http://traditions.gatech.edu/. Mild profanity may be used. Users can ask “What’s the good word?” “How about ‘em dawgs?” or “Tell me a fact.”
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Rambling Wreck, What's the Good Word?
Alexa, ask Rambling Wreck for a fact
name: Georgia Tech Traditions
shortDescription: This skill will answer the question, “What’s the Good Word?” and share facts about Georgia Tech traditions. Mild profanity may be used.
